2.00	Just_a_Little_Girl	Just a Little Girl	"Just a Little Girl" is the debut single from English singer/songwriter Amy Studt. Released on 1 July 2002, the single reached a peak of #14 in the UK Singles Chart. It is taken from Amy's debut album, False Smiles, which was released a year later. The song was used in promotion for the last season of Buffy: The Vampire Slayer. It is included on Now 52 in the UK.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/db/Justalittlegirl.jpg/220px-Justalittlegirl.jpg
